| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4856 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 050a21bd-789c-52bf-9fc4-bfb2694621eb"
